_sText:
Large city map perfect for zombie mod. there is lots of places to hide from zombies and hopefully there is lots of zombies if there is only one human left, so searching goes quicker. just run like hell and find some good places to camp.

also there is some doors which teleport's you on some roof's

this is really a best city map for zombie mod, thats my opinion =D

NOT RECOMMENDING USING BOTS ON THIS MAP, NO .Nav FILES COMING WITH THIS MAP, UNLESS YOU WANT TO WAIT A REALLY LONG LONG LONG TIME SAMPLING WALKABLE SPACE...
(Some Server's Use Bot's On A Zombie Mod)

Hope ya will enjoy the map
